OL,6,FIt came a year after Edwards was named
OL,7,Fas the presenter at the centre of
OL,8,Fallegations he paid a young person for
OL,9,Fsexually explicit photos and resigned
OL,10,Ffrom the BBC "on the basis of medical
OL,11,Fadvice from his doctors".
OL,13,FPolice found no evidence of criminal
OL,14,Fbehaviour in this separate matter.
OL,16,FThe unnamed young man whose contact
OL,17,Fwith Edwards was first exposed by The
OL,18,FSun newspaper, told the Mirror
OL,19,Fnewspaper he "stayed silent for so
OL,20,Flong to protect Huw, but I feel sick
OL,21,Fat what has happened".
