OL,6,FHe said he first contacted the 62-year-
OL,7,Fold newsreader for help, among other
OL,8,Fcelebrities, having spent a few nights
OL,9,Fat a homeless shelter.
OL,11,F"Although it was a friendship at the
OL,12,Fbeginning, it did change. He would say
OL,13,Fthings like, 'Are you going to do
OL,14,Fsomething for me then?' I needed help,
OL,15,Fso I did.
OL,17,F"I feel like he sort of fed on my
OL,18,Fvulnerability...as he knew I needed
OL,19,Fthe money. I felt like I was being
OL,20,Fgroomed."
