OL,6,FThe young man admitted sending
OL,7,Fexplicit messages and videos to
OL,8,FEdwards, who is said to have sent
OL,9,F#35,000 in return over two years.
OL,11,F"Because of who he was as a BBC
OL,12,Fpresenter and because he had such
OL,13,Fpower...I felt like I trusted him and
OL,14,Fthat he cared," the young man said.
OL,16,F"But that's how the manipulation
OL,17,Fstarted. I looked up to this man but
OL,18,Fhe didn't really care about me.
