OL,6,F"I felt like he was taking advantage
OL,7,Fof me but I felt I had to listen to
OL,8,Fhim because he was Huw Edwards."
OL,10,FIt comes as The Sun newspaper
OL,11,Fpublished a video of Edwards waiting
OL,12,Ffor the alleged victim at a Welsh
OL,13,Ftrain station, filmed by the young
OL,14,Fman's stepfather.
OL,16,FThe family of the unnamed young person
OL,17,Foriginally complained to the BBC about
OL,18,FEdwards in May 2023, and he was
OL,19,Fpublicly named by his wife as the TV
OL,20,Fpresenter at the centre of the
OL,21,Fallegations the following July.
