OL,6,FThe young man said he received a text
OL,7,Ffrom an unknown number in October
OL,8,Fafter the events had unfolded, which
OL,9,Fturned out to be Edwards.
OL,11,F"I think it was about two weeks before
OL,12,Fhe got arrested. The message said
OL,13,F'guess who' or something like that,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,F"The message said 'don't say my name
OL,17,Fon here... just call me'. So I phoned
OL,18,Fhim and he said download the messaging
OL,19,Fapp Signal. And he said we can catch
OL,20,Fup on there.
