OL,8,Fremorse for anything at all."
OL,10,FOn Friday, the BBC said Edwards
OL,11,Fresigned from the broadcaster "without
OL,12,Fnotice or financial settlement" during
OL,13,Fa "confidential disciplinary process".
OL,15,FIt comes after two whistleblowers, one
OL,16,Fcurrent and one former BBC worker,
OL,17,Fexpressed disappointment that an
OL,18,Finternal inquiry into Edwards had not
OL,19,Fbeen made public after they alleged
OL,20,Fthey received "inappropriate messages"
OL,21,Ffrom him.
