OL,6,FBefore Edwards resigned, he was the
OL,7,Fbroadcaster's highest-paid newsreader,
OL,8,Fwith a pay bracket between #475,000
OL,9,Fand #479,999 for the year 2023/24,
OL,10,Faccording to the BBC's latest annual
OL,11,Freport.
OL,13,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy urged the
OL,14,Fdisgraced newsreader to "return his
OL,15,Fsalary" and asked the BBC to look into
OL,16,Fwhether it can recoup an estimated
OL,17,F#200,000, which Edwards earned during
OL,18,Fthe period from his arrest in November
OL,19,Funtil his resignation in April.
