OL,6,FMs Nandy told Sky News that she has
OL,7,Fasked to see the employment law advice
OL,8,Fgiven to the BBC, and called for the
OL,9,Fcorporation's director-general Tim
OL,10,FDavie to address "outstanding issues",
OL,11,Fand come back to her next week.
OL,13,FThe minister also said of Edwards: "I
OL,14,Fthink having been arrested on such
OL,15,Fserious charges all the way back in
OL,16,FNovember, to continue to receive that
OL,17,Fsalary all the way through until he
OL,18,Fresigned is wrong and it's not a good
OL,19,Fuse of taxpayers' money.
